OL,7,FTV presenter Gregg Wallace has
OL,8,Fapologised for claiming complaints
OL,9,Fabout his behaviour came from "a
OL,10,Fhandful of middle-class women of a
OL,11,Fcertain age", adding he will now "take
OL,12,Fsome time out".
OL,14,FThe MasterChef presenter, who faces
OL,15,Fvarious allegations including making
OL,16,F"inappropriate sexual jokes", posted a
OL,17,Fvideo on his Instagram stories on
OL,18,FMonday to issue an apology.
