OL,7,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,8,Fspokesman said on Monday: "The Culture
OL,9,FSecretary spoke with the BBC
OL,10,Fleadership at the end of last week on
OL,11,Fthis matter and wider workplace
OL,12,Fculture issues to seek assurances that
OL,13,Fthere are robust processes in place to
OL,14,Fdeal with complaints.
OL,16,F"Clearly the comments we have seen
OL,17,Ffrom the individual over the weekend
OL,18,Fwere completely inappropriate and
OL,19,Fmisogynistic.
